Description:

Buck Adams is in jail, as The World's Greatest Fashion Pimp, a guy who finds beautiful gals and makes sure all his pals get a piece of her on her way to the top. In this case, it's Moana, who, about halfway through the tape gets the Idea and complains, in that lovely Italian accent, "How come everybody you send me to do push-push in my mouth?" How come, indeed? If there's a reason other than helping some horny viewer get his rocks off, it isn't evident in Part 1. See Moana dildoed by Foxxx, double-teamed by Hartley and Wallice, and d.p.'d by Boy and North, while Adams gets to savor Quinn's ass and Sparxx's mouth (what a waste!). The question one has to ask about Part 2 is, who is there left to "push-push"? Sexy in enough spots to make it worth a look
